 When you hear the buzzer, look down at the floor.

18
00:00:43,045 --> 00:00:45,977
 [SOUND] Good.

19
00:00:45,977 --> 00:00:49,063
 This completes the gymnastic portion of your mandatory physical and

20
00:00:49,063 --> 00:00:51,660
 mental wellness exercise.

