00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:52,960
 >> Did you see that?

22
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:55,400
 It was so subtle you might not have even noticed it.

23
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:57,130
 A character in the game asked me to look up.

24
00:00:57,130 --> 00:01:00,360
 The game assumed whichever direction I pressed

25
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:02,850
 was the way I would want to press when I want to look up.

26
00:01:02,850 --> 00:01:04,750
 And set my preference accordingly.

27
00:01:04,750 --> 00:01:07,050
 No option screen, no changing settings.

28
00:01:07,050 --> 00:01:08,230
 The game automatically and

29
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:08,230
 invisibly had me complete my goal of correctly setting my camera preference.

